---
// 8. Audience - who it's for (cards reveal on scroll).
---
<section class="audience" id="audience">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="section__title" data-i18n="audience.title">Lingo7 Realty is for you if you…</h2>
    <div class="audience__grid">
      <div class="audience__card">
        <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#34D399" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
        <span data-i18n="audience.card-english">find the material hard in English → now you read every part with a translation and understand it right away</span>
      </div>
      <div class="audience__card">
        <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#34D399" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
        <span data-i18n="audience.card-failed">have failed before, or are afraid to fail, because of the language → now the questions and answers come in your language too</span>
      </div>
      <div class="audience__card">
        <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#34D399" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
        <span data-i18n="audience.card-retain">worry you will not remember it all → the tests find your weak spots, and the app helps you remember them by exam day</span>
      </div>
      <div class="audience__card">
        <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#34D399" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
        <span data-i18n="audience.card-immigrant">are starting a real estate career as an immigrant → you pass the exam and learn work English at the same time</span>
      </div>
      <div class="audience__card">
        <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#34D399" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
        <span data-i18n="audience.card-time">have little time, just 10 to 15 minutes a day → the book, tests, and math are in one app, in short sessions</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
